---
import { siteConfig } from "../config";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anek+Devanagari:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <title>Terms & Conditions</title>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white text-gray-800">

    <!-- MAIN -->
    <section class="px-6 sm:px-10 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-20 items-start">

        <!-- LEFT -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">

          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-7xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Terms of Service.
          </h2>

          <div
            class="w-[75px] h-[5px] mt-2 rounded-full"
            style={`background-color: ${siteConfig.accentColor}`}
          ></div>

          <p class="text-gray-500 mt-5 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
            Rules, agreements, and responsibilities when using services or working together.
          </p>

        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 w-full min-w-0">

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl 
                      p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12
                      shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">

            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-6">
              Last updated: April 2026
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-8 text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            
              <p>
                By using this website or working with me, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not continue using the site or services.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                All original content on this website—including text, branding, custom visuals, and layout structure—is protected by applicable copyright and intellectual property laws. You may not copy, reproduce, or reuse it without written permission.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                Services are delivered based on an agreed scope. Pricing, timeline, and deliverables are confirmed before work begins. Requests outside the original scope may require additional fees or revised timelines.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                An advance payment may be required to reserve your project slot. Final files are delivered after full payment is received. Unless agreed in writing, payments are non-refundable after work starts.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                Revisions are limited based on your selected package or agreement. Minor changes are included; major direction changes may be treated as separate work.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                Delivery timelines are estimates and may vary with project complexity and feedback speed. Delays caused by missing information or late responses are not my responsibility.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                You are responsible for ensuring that all content, materials, and assets you provide are legally owned or properly licensed. Any legal issues arising from provided content remain your responsibility.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                Once final payment is received, usage rights for final deliverables are transferred to you unless otherwise agreed. I may still display completed work in my portfolio, social media, or promotional materials.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                While I make every effort to ensure quality and reliability, services are provided "as is" without guarantees that they will meet every expectation or perform flawlessly in every context. I am not liable for indirect losses, damages, or business impact resulting from the use of delivered work.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                This website may contain links to third-party platforms or tools. I am not responsible for their content, policies, or practices.
              </p>
            
              <p>
                These terms may be updated from time to time. Continued use of the website or services after updates implies acceptance of the revised terms.
              </p>
            
              <!-- CONTACT -->
              <div class="pt-6">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-base sm:text-lg">
                  Questions about these terms?
                </p>
            
                <p class="text-gray-900 font-medium mt-1">
                  {siteConfig.social.email}
                </p>
              </div>
            
            </div>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </section>

  </body>
</html>
